name: Blog
body:
This is a personal blog which I want to introduce myself and record my life stories. It shows my resume, my universities and my journey from my hometown to HONG KONG, TAIWAN and etc.  

I try to use various special effects of CSS3 and JQuery to make my web pages seems more interesting. Meanwhile, there are still many areas for improvement. 

You can browse my blog by downloading the zip. file or click the link ([BLOG PREVIEWS](http://htmlpreview.github.io/?https://github.com/vicky0203/BLOG/blob/master/main.html)).
note: Don't delete this file! It's used internally to help with page regeneration.
